'''''Kill and Kill Again''''' ni film y'ibikorwa yo mu 1981 iyobowe na Ivan Hall<ref>Film / Kill and Kill Again - TV Tropes <nowiki>https://tvtropes.org</nowiki> › Film</ref>. Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo James Ryan nka Steve Chase wahawe akazi ko gukiza umuhanga Horatio Kane<ref>Kill and Kill Again (Blu-ray) - Kino Lorber Home Video <nowiki>https://www.kinolorber.com</nowiki> › product › kill-and-kill-agai...</ref>, washimuswe n'umuhanga Marduk. Chase akoranya itsinda ryabacanshuro basanga inzira igana ku gihome cy'umugome hanyuma ugasanga barwanira ubuzima bwabo uko bafashwe<ref>Kill and Kill Again | Encyclopedia.com <nowiki>https://www.encyclopedia.com</nowiki> › arts › culture-magazines</ref>.

''Kill and Kill Again'' ni urukurikirane rwa film ''[[:en:Kill_or_Be_Killed_(1980_film)|Kill or Be Killed]]'' kandi yatangiye gufatwa amashusho muri kamena 1980<ref>Kill and Kill Again | Forgotten Films <nowiki>https://forgottenfilmcast.wordpress.com</nowiki> › 2017/12/03</ref>. Iyi filime yafatiwe mu [[Burayi]] no muri [[Amerika]] hamwe n'abakinnyi ahanini bakomoka muri [[Afurika]] y'Epfo<ref>Movies You Should Watch: Kill and Kill Again - Movie Graveyard <nowiki>https://www.mvegraveyard.com</nowiki> › film-reviews › movie...</ref>. Yasohotse i New York ku ya 8 Gicurasi 1981. Yakiriye ibitekerezo bibi byatanzwe na ''Variety'' na ''The New York Times'' basanze filime "idashimishije" kandi ifite "umugambi mubi"<ref>Kill and Kill Again Cast and Crew - Cast Photos and Info <nowiki>https://www.fandango.com</nowiki> › kill-and-kill-again-31245</ref>.

